The paper deals with security and privacy in cellular networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses cryptography methods (cs.IT) and intrusion detection methods (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper deals with privacy-preserving schemes (cs.CY).
